Package: dsJobs
Type: Package
Title: DataSHIELD Durable Federated Job Runtime
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Sarrat González", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "david.sarrat@isglobal.org"),
    person("Juan R", "González", role = "aut", email = "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org"))
Description: Server-side DataSHIELD package for durable federated job execution.
    Provides a two-plane execution model: session-plane steps (DataSHIELD
    assign/aggregate/checkpoint) and artifact-plane steps (processx-isolated
    subprocesses for radiomics, preprocessing, staging). Jobs persist on disk
    via a filesystem-based queue under DSJOBS_HOME, survive session restarts,
    and integrate with dsFlower for Python environments and dsImaging for
    dataset resolution and asset publishing.
